# Capacitor native projects — generated via `npx cap add android` / ios
# locally. Each developer regenerates them; the source of truth is the
# web app + capacitor.config.json. android/ and ios/ folders carry
# machine-specific paths, signing material, and large gradle caches
# we don't want in git.
android/
ios/
.capacitor/
